news.title: Vietnam's No Va Land to hold board meeting amid creditor pressure
news.para: The property developer was urged in September to negotiate a debt restructuring agreement by a group of international creditors with combined 75% ownership of the 2026 unsecured convertible bond.

news.title: China's Country Garden default on dollar bond declared for first time
news.para: Country Garden’s failure to pay interest on the note within a grace period that ended last week “constitutes an event of default,” according to a notice to holders from trustee Citicorp International Ltd seen by Bloomberg News.

news.title: NGT asks Haryana to give list of stone crushers in two districts
news.para: According to a report submitted by the Haryana government to NGT last month, out of the 133 units operating in Mahendergarh, 49 were found to be violating the provisions of a 2016 notification on stone crushers as well as those of the Air (Prevention and Control of Pollution) Act, 1981.
